column12: Hold on, now! Just what do you think I am?
Is this supposed to be some manner of greeting?
Surely you don't see me as some manner of household pet.
How is it that you do not tire of such idiocy?
Yes? Have you a secret you wish to tell me?
What about this do you find so amusing?
Very well. Perhaps I shall regale you with a tale that you will remember forevermore... *ahem*
Must you act so <FONT=ITALIC>familiar</FONT>?
Do you desire the attention of Grimoire Weiss?
How many times must you repeat this pointless activity?
Haven't we more important things we should be doing?
For example, we could be— I say! The great Grimoire Weiss has not finished speaking!
Heavens above, children these days have no respect for their elders...
Stop cavorting about as if you were a child!
I see you've grown quite comfortable around me.
Ah, it's good to see you've developed a reverence for your social betters!
Our journey together has already been a long one, mmm?
Oh, MUST you?
Nothing better to do with your time, I see.
Yes? What is it? What do you want!?
I suppose it couldn't hurt to grace you with my attention every now and again.
You rang?
I suppose a short respite every now and again won't go amiss.
Say what you will about our time together, but it certainly hasn't been dull.
You know, lad, you might consider a relaxing night at home from time to time.
Er, no. Forget I said anything. Let us hurry forth on our next escapade!
If you must play these foolish games with someone, play them with Emil!
Huh!? Why me!?
Oh, but I tire of this insolence. ...Hussy! Open your foul mouth and tell the lad to stop this instant!
I can't wait for your pages to fall out so you'll be reduced to the worthless doorstop you've always been.
Man, why does Weiss get to have all the fun? Must be nice.
Grimoire Weiss would be more than willing to yield this pleasure to you!
Better not. Let him touch you too much and you'll never get the old-man stink off.
A preferable scent to that of a beast-hussy!
What do you want from me? ...Nothing? Feh, so be it.
This is no time for playing about!
Focus on the situation in front of you!
Oh, come now! Stay on your guard!
To think a time would come that I lend you my power.
I was a fool to have expected even the slightest of positive changes from you.
Ah, yes. It's coming back to me. Your unique brand of charm.
My memories have not aged a day.
It has been quite some time, Kainé.
Clearly SOMEONE doesn't have a care in the world.
I understand your fascination with me, but still...
If you are truly that antsy, perhaps you can direct some of that energy to the enemy instead?
If you MUST fondle the great Grimoire Weiss, at least wait to do so until our foes have been vanquished!
Augh! Ack! Be more gentle with me, you heartless brute!
I've had quite enough of your incessant prodding, hussy!
